Name: AI Active
Notes: Blue robot icon - AI providing recommendations

Name: AI Degraded
Notes: Red robot with X - AI in fallback mode

Name: AI Override
Notes: White human icon - Human has overridden AI

Name: OOD Detected
Notes: Warning triangle with robot - Input outside training envelope

Name: OOD Severe
Notes: Red circle with robot - Significant deviation manual required

Name: Learning Enabled
Notes: Book icon - System is learning from operations

Name: Learning Frozen
Notes: Locked book icon - Learning disabled certified config

Name: Cryogenic Hazard
Notes: Snowflake in triangle - Extreme cold hazard -253C

Name: Flammable H2
Notes: Flame with H2 - Flammable hydrogen 4-75% range

Name: High Pressure
Notes: Pressure gauge in triangle - 700 bar warning

Name: Asphyxiation Risk
Notes: Lungs with X - Oxygen displacement hazard

Name: Boil-Off Warning
Notes: Snowflake with arrow up - Boil-off rate indicator

Name: Leak Detection
Notes: Droplet with sensor - H2 leak detected

Name: Venting Active
Notes: Cloud with arrow - Active venting in progress
